  # Search Hotels in Mumbai
  
  Fetches real-time hotel data from Booking.com for Mumbai.
  
  **Response includes:**
  - Hotel ID
  - Hotel name
  - Price (INR)
  - Rating (out of 5)
  - **Hotel URL** ‚Üê Use this to get full details!
  
  **Example Response:**
  ```json
  {
    "hotel_id": 86566,
    "name": "Atlantiis Suites",
    "price": 5879.0,
    "currency": "INR",
    "rating": 4.2,
    "url": "https://www.booking.com/hotel/in/atlantiis-suites.html"
  }
  ```
  
  **Next Step:** Copy the `url` field and use it in request #8 to get full hotel details!
  
  **Note:** First request may take 15-25 seconds (real scraping), subsequent requests are cached.
}
